saait
=====

My mirror of the most boring static page generator.

Meaning of saai (dutch): boring
Pronounciation:          site

Some parts are intentionally hardcoded in C for simplicity.

Original: 
https://www.codemadness.nl/git/stagit
git://git.codemadness.org/stagit

My install
--------

    # apt install libgit2-dev

    $ git clone git://git.codemadness.org/stagit
    $ make
    # make install

    $ echo 'export stagit-html="path-to-stagit-html"' >> $HOME/.bashrc 
    $ source $HOME/.bashrc

My run
------

    $ cd $stagit-html
    $ cd $stagit-html/repo

    $ stagit $HOME/repo
    $ echo "your description" > description

    $ cd ..

Run that for every repo. Then you have your html by stagit
